            <h2>Cappuccino</h2>
            <p><strong>Origin:</strong> Italy</p>
            <p>A balanced coffee with equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and milk foam.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="coffee" id="turkish-coffee">
            <img src="turkish_coffee_image_url" alt="Turkish Coffee">
            <h2>Turkish Coffee</h2>
            <p><strong>Origin:</strong> Turkey</p>
            <p>A rich, unfiltered coffee served with grounds in the cup, often sweetened.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="coffee" id="flat-white">
            <img src="flat_white_image_url" alt="Flat White">
            <h2>Flat White</h2>
            <p><strong>Origin:</strong> Australia/New Zealand</p>
            <p>A smooth, velvety coffee made with espresso and micro-foamed milk.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="coffee" id="americano">
            <img src="americano_image_url" alt="Americano">
            <h2>Americano</h2>
            <p><strong>Origin:</strong> United States</p>
            <p>A diluted espresso that creates a similar strength to brewed coffee.</p>
        </div>
